MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Based on a patch from Felix Hdicke <felixhaedicke@web.de>.
Wine-Bug: https://bugs.winehq.org/show_bug.cgi?id=45277
---
